NAME
    deviation - map the deviations of sample values
 
SYNOPSIS
    #include <acme.h>
    static inherit AcmeStat;
    #include AcmeStatInc
 
    mapping deviation( float *sample );
 
DESCRIPTION
    Returns a mapping of all the values in sample mapped to their
    deviation from the mean.
 
EXAMPLE
    rel_freq( ({ 1, 2, 3 }) -> ([ 1 : 1, 2 : 0, 3 : 1 ])
 
SEE_ALSO
    standard_deviation(A), mean(A)
 
LAST MODIFIED                               
    980502 Devo
